data.Description: Color Options are also available. It is the perfect chair for a passionate gamer, and also for office workers who wish to be more comfortable while they work. The ergonomic computer chair with the high-density memory foam seat, the high backrest, and the adjustable 2D armrests will become your favourite piece of furniture. Material: PVC Leather and Nylon 5-stars Leg Gas lift: Class-3 Dimension: 69 x 52 x (126-35.55) cm Weight: 17.5 Kg Maximum weight capacity: 250 lbs. Function: Lumbar cushion with massage function by using USB connection.
